Inflare provides RDMA streaming primitives for CPU memory, CUDA GPU memory,
and synchronized GPU server chains. CUDA support is enabled by the gpunetio
feature and requires a compatible CUDA/GPUDirect RDMA platform.

Inflare provides CMake targets:

    find_package(inflare CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE inflare::inflare)

Common public headers:

    #include <inflare/cpunetio/cpu_rdma_client.hpp>
    #include <inflare/gpunetio/gpu_rdma_client.hpp>
    #include <inflare/gpunetio/gpu_rdma_server.hpp>
    #include <inflare/gpunetio/gpu_rdma_stream_chain.hpp>
